headline.main: In David Shields’s Brief Essays, People May Be Farther Than They Appear

lead_paragraph: Police questioned Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu for a fourth time on Monday in a corruption investigation that has prompted political rivals to start looking to a "post-Bibi" Israel.
